{"tid":2109100,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I]《Another Eden：穿越時空的貓》(32) 阿姨穿起白衣變成芽衣","createTime":"2020-07-15T03:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T05:54:14.000Z","uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cfecdb7ff3b1d8f213570e4f8d091ee2ce0d62","tid":2109100,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbObRAa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbObRAa.png&h=3a60600d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOVMfNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOVMfNQ.jpg&h=46aed113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdGg5vS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdGg5vS.jpg&h=993afb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sX16axB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsX16axB.jpg&h=c18cf67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/698009331756433438/kv_pc.jpg?width=1124&amp;height=598\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F698009331756433438%2Fkv_pc.jpg%3Fwidth%3D1124%26height%3D598&h=429e2908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/653960908934217728/9.png?width=1440&amp;height=600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F653960908934217728%2F9.png%3Fwidth%3D1440%26height%3D600&h=411a9a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/653960903531692032/10.png?width=400&amp;height=168\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F653960903531692032%2F10.png%3Fwidth%3D400%26height%3D168&h=77d71a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evp9s2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fevp9s2r.png&h=beed4a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ.建唔建議首抽?<br />\n<br />\nA.唔建議,因為刷一次首抽要差唔多30分鐘,要5星奶開局不如8591/淘寶<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.首抽抽咩好<br />\n<br />\nA.5星奶/火補 風補 國王AS &gt;其次水劍(謝奈), 水法(麥提/AS), 巫女(由奈 原版/AS) 基本上宜家有五星就練<br />\n<br />\n基本上大部分五星都有用, 不過你要最勁既就果幾隻<br />\n<br />\n奶: 瑪莉，風補(補+必爆+加速+buff) 或者 火補(蘿潔塔) (補.法攻.異常盾)<br />\n<br />\n物理打手: 火錘專武 水槍 水母 (娜基AS 一拳超人) 忍者(燕) 茜AS 蝶火女 (蘇賽特, 有專武會用原版多) 阿佐美 (配顯現專武) etc. (紫央專武收皮)<br />\n<br />\n法師:水法 (麥提/AS) 有專武用原版都勁<br />\n<br />\n輔助: 巫女(尤奈) 風補<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇得同人玩?<br />\n<br />\nA.冇,只係一隻單機到GAME,抽到5星唔洗拎上黎曬,冇人想知<br />\n<br />\n(其實都可以既 大家一齊開心. 不過唔知會唔會引起其他人暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.副本係咩黎?<br />\n<br />\nA.係次元裂縫入面可以打到角色既職業書,升星書<br />\n<br />\n每日0500、1100、1700、2300時會回復1張綠票1張紅票。<br />\n<br />\n打完第11章,係次元就會開放HARD難度<br />\n<br />\n打完第25章,係次元就會開放VERY HARD難度<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【心得】副本系統須知、天冥值介紹及角色升星(升級)職業書出處(更新國際版V2.1.4) (取自巴哈 貓友)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770&amp;tnum=113&amp;bPage=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26snA%3D770%26tnum%3D113%26bPage%3D3&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=74a89229\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770&amp;tnum=113&amp;bPage=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ.爆左主線之後有咩做<br />\n<br />\nA.百討 釣魚 外傳 礦坑 清票 隱王<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.過左劇情,d怪打唔返點算?<br />\n<br />\nA.去次元夾縫左邊度門,有得入返去打過左既劇情<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.主角群洗唔洗升5星<br />\n<br />\nA.升啦,推薦升男主,大波艾美。而青蛙,海蕾娜,莉卡, 魔王 都有得上5星 (日服),係爭阿妹未有. 而邂逅角 (阿佐美, 迦琉, 思琳) 優先用夢書升5星 因為你唔會有機會抽到佢地5星<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.邊到打最多經<br />\n<br />\nA. 封域打經驗關 有紅票綠票版<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.角色能力盤點數夠唔夠用?<br />\n<br />\nA.當你最高lv時,夠你點曬佢<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.戰鬥相關問題<br />\n<br />\nA.力量-物攻<br />\n<br />\n智力-魔攻,補量<br />\n<br />\n耐力-物防<br />\n<br />\n精神-魔防<br />\n<br />\n速度-行動順序<br />\n<br />\n幸運-爆擊率 (法師法攻本身冇爆擊 升幸運聲稱可以減低被爆擊率)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇攻略網站推介<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://A.https\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FA.https&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=bee8bbca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://A.https</a>://<a href=\"http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/[/url][/url][/url][/url][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.gaym.jp%2FiPhone%2Fanother-eden%2F%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=302fff72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/[/url][/url][/url][/url][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/anaden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fanaden%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=7b472a7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/anaden/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FB.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26subbsn%3D0&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=7dea1b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0</a> 巴哈<br />\n<br />\n 問問題工具 <a href=\"https://magic-panda-engineer.github.io/another_picker/index.html?fbclid=IwAR0N71NE0Y5_B6LZlahmrDWSGR0LdJrj3UnkOHIw6FwWj-BP8m-7-AHm7jg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmagic-panda-engineer.github.io%2Fanother_picker%2Findex.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0N71NE0Y5_B6LZlahmrDWSGR0LdJrj3UnkOHIw6FwWj-BP8m-7-AHm7jg&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a441a973\" target=\"_blank\">https://magic-panda-engineer.github.io/another_picker/index.html?fbclid=IwAR0N71NE0Y5_B6LZlahmrDWSGR0LdJrj3UnkOHIw6FwWj-BP8m-7-AHm7jg</a><br />\n<br />\nQ.仲有冇其他野要注意?<br />\n<br />\nA.除左信箱每日送20石之外,買石個到仲有廣告10石拎,總共30石<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nQ. 可唔可以用電腦模擬器玩?<br />\n<br />\nA. 可以, 但係如果你用模擬器平台玩但係出左任何問題, 官方都有權唔幫你． 同埋如果有人想同一個帳號又玩模擬器又玩手機，建議唔好, 24小時內只可以引繼 3 - 4次, 第四次 好似 會被ban 24小時.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57vCUZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57vCUZU.png&h=5c065dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住攻略打輕鬆啲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=3743&amp;bpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26snA%3D3743%26bpage%3D1&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=c9eb8f8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=3743&amp;bpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"813c147bc3354b4dc61680b1853549baa6627af5","tid":2109100,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"as火補<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddeac0cf01d8c966ddd401d2b6eb3b81354e332","tid":2109100,"uid":63357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMrhaSe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMrhaSe.png&h=5a53438e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iznPMqA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiznPMqA.png&h=5a752dca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n隻game係咪有bug，連續兩場出夢書，前兩日又係咁，我想要異節呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"